              <svg class="h-5 w-5 text-green-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/>
              </svg>
              Envío Gratuito
            </h3>
